* Build core and tests:
make

* Run the Swing GUI:
. ./env
java torrefactor.ui.swing.SwingClient
**FIXME: The "Start Downloading" and "Stop Downloading" menu items only work
  when a torrent is selected, otherwise they do nothing. They should be
  disabled when not usabled.**

* Run tests:
make runtest

* Run the test client:
. ./env
java test.Client <input.torrent> <output directory>


* Build the experimental and not usable Qt GUI:
- Install QtJambi and get the jar into your CLASSPATH
make src.torrefactor.ui.qt

* Run the Qt GUI:
. ./env
java torrefactor.ui.qt.Main
